WhatsApp Confirms Sudden Backup Passkey Security Move For Billions

Passkeys are not new, but they are still facing challenges as far as transitioning from passwords is concerned. Given the number of password leaks, including the latest 183 million credentials shocker, anything that major brands can do to advance the use of highly secure passkeys is, erm, key to making security progress. 

Now, WhatsApp has suddenly announced a feature that helps tremendously in this regard: passkey-encrypted backups for Android and iOS users. Here’s what you need to know. https://t.co/r8LpAdgglq
